Typora Export to HTML Mixin平常喜欢用Typora编写Markdown笔记，一般来说都是导出为pdf方便阅读，有时候也导出为html文件方便直接放在静态网站上展示。 偶然发现Typora可以在导出的html文件的&lt;head&gt;和&lt;body&gt;中插入自定义代码。这就有了很多可玩性。 1. 官方文档这样说 Add Custom ContentsYou can add custom contents in Append in and Append in , which will be inserted into part and part in the exported html. For contents that cannot be added into , even when it is added in Append in , it will be prepend into instead. Same for Append in . Export YAML metaVariables like $&#123;title&#125; or $&#123;author&#125; in &lt;title&gt; and &lt;meta&gt; tag will be replaced by corresponding variables defined in YAML Front Matter. For example, you can insert additional &lt;meta&gt; data or custom &lt;style&gt; into exported html using those options, e.g: 123&lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;author&quot; content=&quot;$&#123;author&#125;&quot;&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;description&quot; content=&quot;$&#123;description&#125;&quot;&gt; To use those variables in somewhere else, you can add some javascript in Append in &lt;body /&gt;, to read target meta tag, and modified export content as you want. 2. 实践官方文档中有几点需要注意 变量可以写在Markdown的YAML头注释中，输入方式是三个减号---并return Typora只能在&lt;head&gt;中插入带变量的内容，如果需要在&lt;body&gt;中使用变量，需要先在&lt;head&gt;中通过&lt;meta&gt;引入，在&lt;body&gt;中通过Javascript读取&lt;meta&gt;中的变量再使用。 输出user agent在&lt;body&gt;中 12345678910&lt;script&gt;if(navigator.userAgentData)&#123;var ua = navigator.userAgentData.platform || &quot;Unknown&quot;;ua = ua + &quot; &quot; + navigator.userAgentData.brands[2].brand + &quot; var.&quot; + navigator.userAgentData.brands[2].version;console.log(&quot;%c&quot;+ua, &quot;font-size:16px;background-color:black;color:white;padding:4px;margin:4px;&quot;);&#125;else&#123;var ua = navigator.userAgent;console.log(&quot;%c&quot;+ua, &quot;font-size:16px;background-color:black;color:white;padding:4px;margin:4px;&quot;);&#125;&lt;/script&gt; 注意⚠️，userAgentData是新属性 效果 输出title在&lt;head&gt;中 1&lt;title&gt;$&#123;title&#125;&lt;/title&gt; 在&lt;body&gt;中 1234&lt;script&gt;var title = document.getElementsByTagName(&#x27;title&#x27;)[0].textContent;console.log(&quot;%c&quot;+&quot;Title: &quot;+title, &quot;font-size:16px;background-color:black;color:white;padding:4px;margin:4px;&quot;);&lt;/script&gt; 效果 输出自定义变量在&lt;head&gt;中 1&lt;meta name=&quot;description&quot; content=&quot;$&#123;description&#125;&quot;&gt; 在&lt;body&gt;中 1234&lt;script&gt;var desp = document.getElementsByTagName(&#x27;meta&#x27;)[&#x27;description&#x27;].content;console.log(&quot;%c&quot;+&quot;Desp: &quot;+desp, &quot;font-size:16px;background-color:white;color:black;padding:4px;margin:4px;&quot;);&lt;/script&gt; 效果 输出本页地址在&lt;body&gt;中 1234&lt;script&gt;var pageUrl = window.location.href;console.log(&quot;%cPlease indicate the URL for forwarding: &quot;+ pageUrl, &quot;font-size:18px;background-color:yellow;color:black;padding:4px;margin:4px;&quot;)&lt;/script&gt; 进阶：复制页面文本时添加版权信息 12345678910111213141516171819202122&lt;script&gt;function addLink()&#123; var pageUrl = window.location.href; var linkContent = &quot;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Please indicate the URL for forwarding: &lt;br/&gt;
&quot;+ pageUrl+&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;; var selected = selection = window.getSelection() ? window.getSelection() : document.selection.createRange().text; if(window.clipboardData)&#123; window.clipboardData.setData (&quot;Text&quot;, selected+linkContent); &#125;else&#123; var newDiv = document.createElement(&#x27;div&#x27;); newDiv.style.position =&#x27;absolute&#x27;; newDiv.style.left =&#x27;-99999px&#x27;; newDiv.style.top =&#x27;-99999px&#x27;; document.body.appendChild(newDiv); newDiv.innerHTML = selected+linkContent; selection.selectAllChildren(newDiv); window.setTimeout(function() &#123; document.body.removeChild(newDiv); &#125;,0); &#125;&#125;document.oncopy = addLink;&lt;/script&gt; 3. 完因为是内嵌代码，理论上是支持一切网页上可以运行的内容。可以自行发掘用法。 一次设定，导出无忧。 我的&lt;script&gt;使用uglify压缩 1var ua,title=document.getElementsByTagName(&quot;title&quot;)[0].textContent,updatetime=document.getElementsByTagName(&quot;meta&quot;).updatetime.content,pageUrl=(console.log(&quot;%cTitle: &quot;+title+&quot;
